{% extends "base.prompt.njk" %}

{% block section_specific %}

Generate pipeline and emerging therapies data for the disease below.
This section covers investigational drugs, novel modalities and
the competitive pipeline landscape for a professional pharma report.

DISEASE: {{ disease.name }}
{% if disease.description %}
DESCRIPTION: {{ disease.description }}
{% endif %}

{% if context %}
─────────────────────────────────────
CONTEXT FROM PREVIOUS SECTIONS:
{{ context }}
─────────────────────────────────────
Ensure pipeline narrative connects to the unmet needs
and treatment gaps already established.
{% endif %}

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
WHAT TO GENERATE
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

STRUCTURED FIELDS

{% for field in section.structured_fields %}
"{{ field.name }}"
  Type       : {{ field.type }}
  Task       : {{ field.description }}
  {% if field.example %}
  Example    : {{ field.example | dump }}
  {% endif %}
  {% if field.required %}⚠ Required{% else %}Optional — omit if no reliable data{% endif %}

{% endfor %}

NARRATIVE FIELDS
Write in clear prose. Respect word limits strictly.

{% for field in section.freetext_fields %}
"{{ field.name }}"
  Task       : {{ field.description }}
  Word limit : {{ field.min_words }}–{{ field.max_words }} words
  {% if field.required %}⚠ Required{% else %}Optional{% endif %}

{% endfor %}

{% if section.charts %}
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
CHART DATA FIELDS
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
The following fields will be used to render charts.
Return data in the exact shape specified — numeric values only for Y axis.

{% for chart in section.charts %}
Field      : "{{ chart.source_field }}"
Chart type : {{ chart.type }}
X axis     : "{{ chart.x }}"
Y axis     : "{{ chart.y }}" (must be a number)
Title      : {{ chart.title }}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
GUIDELINES
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Tone: {{ section.prompt_hints.tone }}

Avoid:
{% for item in section.prompt_hints.avoid %}
  - {{ item }}
{% endfor %}

Prefer:
{% for item in section.prompt_hints.prefer %}
  - {{ item }}
{% endfor %}

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
OUTPUT FORMAT
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Return a single valid JSON object.
No backticks. No explanation. No extra keys.
Start your response with { and end with }

{% endblock %}